General bug fixes and improvements Introducing Filmm 3.0! More features coming soon!

New FREE blur tool! Soften overly digital footage with our new blur tool in Adjust for a dreamier vintage look From Filmm 2.0! New multi clip editing: Add as many videos or images to your project as you like Run filters effects and adjustments on all clips at once or edit individually Simple drag drop to reorder Now you can cut duplicate or reverse a clip Professional transitions: Pick from 28 expertly designed options within the new Clips menu Choose classic animations or more advanced analog inspired blends Recent projects: Come back to any edit at any time as they re now stored in Recent Projects Preview duplicate rename or remove projects as needed Monthly Filmm subscription! If year feels like a little too much you now can choose our monthly option to get unlimited access to Filmm features indefinitely We ve got even more in store for this little app. Thank you all so much for your support!
